Insider Activity


Individual




David R. Carlucci



Mr. David R. Carlucci is Independent Director at Mallinckrodt Plc, Independent Director at MasterCard, Inc., and Independent Director at MasterCard International, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Mallinckrodt Plc, MasterCard, Inc., and MasterCard International, Inc.
Mr. Carlucci was previously employed as Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by IMS Health, Inc., General Manager by IBM Printing Systems Division, Vice President-Marketing & Channel Management by IBM PC Co., and General Manager-Americas by International Business Machines Corp.
He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Rochester.



